> > Does this work?
> > myjobs=3D();for a (${(k)jobstates})
> > {j=3D$jobstates[$a];myjobs+=3D($a"${${(@s,:,)j}[2]}")};myjobs=3D${(j:,:=
)myjobs}
>=20
> whooa! :-) it does work.

fyi: it needed one small tweak, if you have more than 2 bg jobs:

    myjobs=3D()
    for a (${(k)jobstates})
    {j=3D$jobstates[$a];i=3D"${${(@s,:,)j}[2]}"
    myjobs+=3D(a${i//[^+-]/})}
#              ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
#        filter out anything but + or -
    myjobs=3D${(j:,:)myjobs}


